{"tid":500828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支付寶正式進駐港鐵！羅湖落馬洲買飛都用到","createTime":"2017-12-16T07:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T07:53:19.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f78355f0269b517e62ec135fc2d8d0d426b5e845","tid":500828,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171216/large/1513408002_9cb4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171216%2Flarge%2F1513408002_9cb4.png&h=bf87eee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前消息指，支付寶母公司螞蟻金服擬於港鐵推動透過支付寶買車票。今日（16日）支付寶於官方微博正式宣佈，港鐵乘客及遊客均可以在羅湖站及落馬洲站，用支付寶或支付寶HK購買車票。<br />\n<br />\n支付寶表示由今日開始，乘客可使用支付寶於港鐵站購買單程票，但只限於羅湖及落馬洲兩個過境口岸站，為乘客及內地遊客提供更多的付款選擇。於落馬洲站，目前只有一部售票機可用支付寶付款，不少來港旅客向職員詢問用法。支付寶購買單程車票以港元為單位，價格亦與用現金購買單程車票一樣。"},{"pid":"468e52766e628ddbbb0081d2875d12b26f059ba2","tid":500828,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"928a829b507e7b1ddb527cf9f3e45a9829c2e015","tid":500828,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1ee8b39c4caa7846fdb4c40ec35f71f6b2c1bd","tid":500828,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多個選擇幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人口戰術<br />\n<br />\n八達通遲早消失"},{"pid":"ea584739db8498e3c20d557c5ebbc04643decf92","tid":500828,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eb86cbe71c09d2e882734509723098f480e642","tid":500828,"uid":59695,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔撚用支那嘢"},